data.description: Welcome to 3399 King Springs - a truly magnificent home that effortlessly combines luxury, comfort, and functionality. This 6 bedroom, 5 full/2 half bathroom home boasts an array of amenities that make it stand out in the highly sought after Smyrna area. As you approach the property, the allure of the all brick exterior is undeniable. A sense of grandeur is immediately established, setting the tone for what awaits within. The expansive gated driveway, designed to accommodate plenty of parking, leads you to an impressive 1,800 square foot 3 car garage - a haven for car or motorcycle enthusiasts or those who simply appreciate ample storage space. The main floor welcomes you with the timeless elegance of hardwoods throughout. A separate dining room invites intimate gatherings, while the 2 story living room creates an open and airy atmosphere. Many possibilities exist with the double door office - a perfect space for remote work or a quiet retreat. A bedroom with a full bath ensures convenience, while a powder room adds a touch of sophistication. Prepare to be captivated by the heart of the home - a kitchen that defines modern luxury. Recently remodeled in 2024, this masterpiece features a breakfast bar, double oven, and a custom-built refrigerator. The attention to detail is unparalleled, making this kitchen a dream for both cooking enthusiasts and seasoned entertainers alike. Step outside into the serenity of this private oasis. Here, the pool invites you to cool off on warm summer days, and either the screened in porch, open air deck, or tiled patio set the stage for gatherings both day and night. Venture upstairs, where large windows bathe the bedrooms in natural light. The master suite is a sanctuary of its own, complete with an attached office, expansive walk-in closets, his and hers vanities, a whirlpool tub, and a stunning shower. Convenience meets luxury with an upstairs laundry room, ensuring that daily tasks are a breeze. The lowest level unveils additional surprises, with a bedroom, full bath, half bath, office/exercise room, storage room, and a second eat-in kitchen. The family room hosts the third fireplace, while a soundproof workshop caters to those with creative or hobbyist inclinations. The meticulous design and attention to detail are evident in every corner, making this lowest level an extension of the home's excellence. Upgrades are sprinkled throughout, enhancing the property's value and desirability. The newly remodeled kitchen, enticing pool, tiled patio, and all new windows are just a few of the enhancements that set this home apart. This residence is a testament to the finer things, where luxury meets functionality, and every detail is designed with your utmost enjoyment in mind.
